public abstract class StateDependentInputVerifier
extends TextFieldInputVerifier
implements Cloneable

StateDependentInputVerifier is an extension of TextFieldInputVerifier common to text fields whose validation depends on the current values of other parameters or perhaps on other aspects of IDEA's current state.
